# Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of primary sources and the potential bias in historical interpretations. The perspectives included are based on available literature and may not encompass all viewpoints. Additionally, the moral and ethical implications of the bombing are subjective and can vary significantly based on individual values and historical context.